  "description": "A morphism class in the predicate category, induced by the swap (s, o) ↦ (o, s) on the entity-pair index. Encodes the relational converse: the predicate p^c holds at the pair (s, o) exactly where p holds at (o, s). One of the four canonical generators of the predicate category.",
